This paper presents a model of online learning with partial information feedback, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of graph structured feedback also suggests a focus on graph theory and network analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
